\int_a^b f(t)+g(t)\,dt=\int_a^b u_f(t)+iv_f(t)+u_g(t)+iv_g(t)\,dt=\int_a^b u_f(t)+iv_f(t)\,dt+\int_a^b u_g(t)+iv_g(t)\,dt=\int_a^b f(t)\,dt+\int_a^b g(t)\,dt
a\int_a^b f(t)\,dt=(x+iy)\int_a^b u(t)+iv(t)\,dt=(x+iy)\int_a^b u(t)\,dt+(x+iy)i\int_a^b v(t)\,dt=x\int_a^b u(t)\,dt+iy \int_a^b u(t)\,dt+ix\int_a^b v(t)\,dt-y\int_a^b v(t)\,dt=\int_a^b xu(t)\,dt+i\int_a^b xv(t)\,dt+i\int_a^b yu(t)\,dt-\int_a^b yv(t)\,dt=\int_a^b xu(t)\,dt-\int_a^b y v(t)\,dt+i \int_a^b x v(t)\,dt+i\int_a^b yu(t)\,dt=\int_a^b a f(t)\,dt
